o-boost-medical-supplies%2Famp_articleshow%2F105533547.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sale%20Of%20Houses%20Over%20Rs%204%20Crore%20Doubles%2C%20Most%20Growth%20Seen%20In%20This%20City%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESale%20of%20luxury%20homes%20worth%20Rs%204%20crore%20and%20more%20jumped%2097%20per%20cent%20year-on-year%20in%20the%20seven%20major%20cities%20of%20India%20between%20January%20and%20September%202023%2C%20a%20report%20from%20real%20estate%20firm%20CBRE%20said%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20accounted%20for%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20luxury%20housing%20sales%20in%20the%20period.%20Delhi-NCR%20accounted%20for%2037%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20sales%2C%20Mumbai%20for%2035%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20for%2018%20per%20cent.%20Pune%20accounted%20for%20the%20remaining%204%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20propelled%20the%20surge%20in%20luxury%20housing%20sales%2C%20including%20a%20robust%20economy%2C%20burgeoning%20disposable%20incomes%2C%20an%20aspiration%20for%20enhanced%20living%20standards%2C%20and%20a%20dearth%20of%20luxury%20residences%20in%20major%20metropolitan%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBRE%20said%20that%20the%20festive%20season%20of%20October%20to%20December%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20further%20growth%20in%20luxury%20housing%20sales.%20The%20firm%20said%20that%20it%20expects%20the%20number%20of%20first-time%20luxury%20home%20buyers%20to%20increase%20in%20the%20October-December%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20reason%20for%20this%20spike%20is%20rising%20aspirations%20and%20a%20growing%20Indian%20economy.%20Incentives%20by%20developers%20and%20smart%20home%20technologies%20such%20as%20smart%20switches%20and%20controlling%20lighting%20and%20other%20things%20with%20a%20click%20on%20the%20phone%20are%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20this%20surge%20in%20luxury%20home%20sales%2C%20besides%20the%20post-pandemic%20need%20for%20larger%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20CBRE%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomic%20growth%2C%20favorable%20regulatory%20measures%2C%20and%20evolving%20lifestyle%20preferences%20will%20see%20a%20surge%20in%20residential%20sales%20and%20new%20launches%20within%20the%20premium%20and%20luxury%20housing%20segment%2C%20potentially%20reaching%20a%2010-year%20high%20in%202023%2C%20the%20CBRE%20report%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20buyers%20seek%20more%20spacious%20living%20post-pandemic%2C%20the%20influx%20of%20smart%20home%20technology%20and%20developer-backed%20incentives%20is%20driving%20a%20boom%20in%20luxury%20home%20sales%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20upsurge%20is%20driven%20by%20the%20growing%20appeal%20of%20luxury%20homes%20among%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20(HNIs)%20and%20non-resident%20Indians%20(NRIs)%20who%20seek%20secure%20and%20rewarding%20investment%20opportunities%2C%20CBRE%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20trends%20suggest%20that%20luxury%20homes%20are%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20important%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20real%20estate%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701080580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp69qa1m8_luxury-home-generic-pixabay-_625x300_27_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsale-of-houses-worth-over-rs-4-crore-up-by-97-delhi-ncr-accounts-for-4609734%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sale%20of%20luxury%20homes%20worth%20Rs%204%20crore%20and%20more%20jumped%2097%20per%20cent%20year-on-year%20in%20the%20seven%20major%20cities%20of%20India%20between%20January%20and%20September%202023%2C%20a%20report%20from%20real%20estate%20firm%20CBRE%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsale-of-houses-worth-over-rs-4-crore-up-by-97-delhi-ncr-accounts-for-4609734%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.