er%20this%20year.%20There%2C%20too%2C%20Modi%20led%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20and%20made%20the%20election%20all%20about%20himself.%20Before%20the%20memory%20of%20that%20loss%20has%20even%20begun%20to%20fade%2C%20he%20has%20once%20again%20made%20these%20state%20elections%20all%20about%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20could%20be%20that%20since%202014%2C%20Modi%20has%20sought%20to%20project%20a%20regal%20aura%20%E2%80%93%20he%20sees%20himself%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98elected%20monarch%E2%80%99%20of%20India.%20And%20perhaps%20he%20wants%20his%20image%20in%20the%20public%20mind%20at%20all%20times.%20This%20is%20not%20for%20electoral%20reasons%20alone%3A%20he%20wants%20to%20make%20every%20discourse%20in%20India%20about%20himself.%20In%20fact%2C%20Indian%20citizens%20cannot%20escape%20his%20presence%20even%20in%20municipal%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20after%20all%2C%20people%20have%20seen%20him%20putting%20his%20reputation%20at%20stake%20even%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-hails-bjp-s-win-in-goa-municipal-elections-101616432760568.html%5C%22%3Elocal%20body%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20to%20keep%20public%20discussion%20focused%20on%20himself.%20Modi%20alone%20is%20the%20agenda%20setter%20and%20subject%20of%20public%20discourse.%20All%20opposition%20parties%20are%20forced%20to%20respond%20to%20him%2C%20because%20he%20is%20the%20authoritative%20voice%20and%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20party.%20Thus%20emerges%20the%20image%20of%20a%20single%20warrior%20battling%20scores%20of%20adversaries%2C%20which%20in%20itself%20is%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20reason%20for%20Modi%20keeping%20the%20electoral%20focus%20on%20himself%20could%20be%20to%20project%20himself%20as%20the%20personification%20of%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ci%3EVikas%20Purush%3C%2Fi%3E%20or%20%E2%80%98Development%20Man%E2%80%99.%20And%20yet%20he%20seems%20to%20give%20himself%20the%20freedom%2C%20whenever%20needed%2C%20to%20run%20an%20election%20campaign%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwith-modis-blessing-bjps-communal-agenda-gets-a-boost-in-coastal-karnataka%5C%22%3Edivides%20the%20electorate%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20communal%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20can%20be%20crass%20and%20anti-Muslim%20in%20his%20election%20speeches%2C%20but%20his%20position%20as%20prime%20minister%20prevents%20public%20criticism.%20In%20the%20recently%20held%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20he%20even%20raised%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmangaluru%2Fpm-modi-raises-pitch-against-congress-proposal-to-ban-bajrang-dal%2Farticleshow%2F99979517.cms%5C%22%3Eslogan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20militant%20outfits%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20the%20fount%20of%20Hindu%20nationalist%20politics.%20There%20was%20no%20public%20uproar.%20Even%20a%20cursory%20look%20at%20his%20election%20speeches%20would%20reveal%20that%20he%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F918630%2Fthe-daily-fix-goodbye-vikas-modi-and-the-bjp-have-decided-to-run-an-explicitly-communal-campaign%5C%22%3Econsistently%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20largely%20uncritical%20media%20appears%20to%20give%20him%20a%20free%20pass%20for%20his%20divisive%20electioneering%2C%20perhaps%20dismissing%20his%20communal%20rhetoric%20as%20electoral%20compulsion.%20When%20Modi%20is%20engaged%20in%20an%20electoral%20battle%2C%20it%20almost%20appears%20as%20if%20the%20media%20joins%20forces%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20always%20a%20winning%20formula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20projection%20of%20Modi%20as%20the%20sole%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20always%20lead%20to%20electoral%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202015.%20Delhi%20was%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20to%20elect%20the%20legislative%20assembly.%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20been%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20for%20barely%20nine%20months%20and%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98Modi%20wave%E2%80%99%20was%20in%20full%20flow.%20Delhi%20is%20not%20even%20a%20full%20state%2C%20yet%20Modi%2C%20the%20supreme%20leader%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20his%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fassembly-elections-2015%2Fdelhi%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-election-results-kejriwal-aap-sweeps-delhi-bjp-modi-239638-2015-02-10%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20had%20made%20Delhi%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%20with%20a%20massive%20ad%20blitzkrieg%20asking%20for%20votes%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20an%20aggressive%20campaign%20telling%20the%20electorate%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20BJP%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20then%20those%20here%20will%20be%20afraid%20of%20Modi%20and%20the%20central%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20BJP%20lost%20badly.%20Their%20defeat%20under%20Modi%20was%20massive%2C%20with%20the%20party%20slumping%20to%20just%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20from%20its%20earlier%20tally%20of%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20rushed%20to%20clarify%20that%20it%20was%20merely%20a%20state%20election%20fought%20on%20local%20issues%20and%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20referendum%20on%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20the%20Delhi%20debacle%2C%20Modi%20led%20another%20election%20campaign%20%E2%80%93%20this%20time%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20was%20going%20to%20the%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20lost%20again.%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Findia-bihar-election-result-jdu-bjp-modi-idUSKCN0SX04P20151108%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20suffered%20a%20heavy%20defeat%20on%20Sunday%20in%20an%20election%20in%20Bihar%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20third%20most-populous%20state%2C%20signalling%20the%20waning%20power%20of%20a%20leader%20who%20until%20recently%20had%20an%20unrivalled%20reputation%20as%20a%20vote%20winner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20myth%20of%20Modi%20as%20an%20unbeatable%20political%20leader%20has%20been%20broken%20again%20and%20again%20in%20the%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20elections.%20Be%20it%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20or%20the%20northeastern%20states%20like%20Manipur%20and%20Meghalaya%2C%20the%20BJP%20lost%20despite%20Modi%20being%20its%20chief%20campaigner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Modi%20did%20after%20losing%20the%20elections%20was%20to%20break%20the%20opposition%20parties%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-has-lost-six-governments-to-bjp-since-pm-narendra-modi-assumed-power-in-2014-954411.html%5C%22%3Edefections%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20essentially%20%E2%80%98buying%20up%E2%80%99%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20legislators%20to%20topple%20the%20elected%20government.%20He%20thus%20snatched%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20even%20after%20losing%20the%20elections.%20These%20developments%20were%20presented%20as%20master%20strokes%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20who%20could%20turn%20electoral%20defeats%20into%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20significant%20that%20in%20the%20current%20elections%20in%20five%20states%2C%20he%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20address%20even%20a%20single%20meeting%20in%20Mizoram%20as%20the%20decimation%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20seems%20certain%20%E2%80%93%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20unpopularity%20among%20the%20Mizos.%20After%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20insensitive%20handling%20of%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur%2C%20tribal%20communities%20displaced%20