20the%20Telangana%20Assembly%20election%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Thursday%20and%20the%20model%20code%20will%20stay%20in%20force%20till%20December%203%2C%20when%20the%20counting%20will%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20letter%20to%20the%20poll%20body%2C%20the%20BRS%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20submitted%20that%20Shri%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20has%20not%20made%20any%20such%20comment%20which%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20your%20order%20dated%2025.11.2023.%20He%20merely%20thanked%20your%20authority%20for%20allowing%20the%20disbursement%20of%20scheme%20amount%20to%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Telangana.%20This%20statement%20of%20Shri%20T%20Harish%20Rao%20is%20an%20inadvertent%20statement%20and%20nothing%20but%20an%20expression%20of%20gratitude%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20farmers%20have%20begun%20cultivation%20for%20the%20rabi%20season%20and%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20has%20been%20on%20since%20the%20past%20five-and-a-half%20years.%20The%20party%20said%20that%20disbursal%20is%20being%20allowed%20under%20the%20Union%20government's%20PM%20Kisan%20scheme%20and%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20both%20the%20schemes%20so%20far%20as%20assistance%20to%20the%20farmers%20is%20considered%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stoppage%20of%20disbursement%20would%20cause%20irreparable%20loss%20to%20the%20farmers%20since%20the%20agricultural%20season%20would%20be%20lost.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20request%20you%20to%20take%20a%20right%20view%20and%20withdraw%20the%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701077460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2F1kpjqlto_farming-generic-650_625x300_07_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-rythu-bandhu-irreparable-loss-for-farmers-brs-on-poll-body-order-pausing-aid-4609735%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22