%20three%20and%20described%20the%20feeling%20of%20working%20with%20professionals%20who%20bring%20out%20the%20best%20in%20others%20as%20%26quot%3Bincredible%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20elaborating%20on%20this%20point%2C%20he%20talked%20about%20the%20significance%20of%20collaboration%20and%20counted%20it%20as%20a%20crucial%20skill.%20The%20Apple%20CEO%20expressed%20that%20when%20evaluating%20individuals%2C%20one%20of%20the%20traits%20he%20seeks%20is%20their%20ability%20to%20collaborate%20effectively.%20He%20articulated%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Can%20they%20really%20collaborate%3F%20Do%20they%20deeply%20believe%20that%201%20plus%201%20equals%20three%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20people%20need%20a%20degree%20or%20great%20coding%20skills%20to%20work%20at%20the%20tech%20giant%2C%20he%20replied%20that%20Apple%20welcomes%20individuals%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds.%20He%20clarified%20that%20this%20inclusivity%20encompasses%20both%20those%20with%20and%20without%20a%20college%20degree.%20While%20Mr%20Cook%20acknowledged%20the%20value%20of%20coding%20as%20a%20beneficial%20skill%2C%20he%20highlighted%20that%20Apple%20has%20recruited%20individuals%20who%20may%20not%20possess%20extensive%20coding%20expertise%20or%20regularly%20engage%20in%20coding%20as%20part%20of%20their%20daily%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20skill%20that%20he%20looks%20for%20in%20Apple%20employees%2C%20Mr%20Cook%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20curious%20people%20who%20are%20not%20afraid%20of%20asking%20questions.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20he%20looks%20for%20people%20who%20are%20creative%20and%20team%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20podcast%2C%20he%20also%20spoke%20about%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20He%20said%20the%20technology%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Blife-changing%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20can%20help%20people%20fix%20problems%20and%20has%20vast%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701076140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim