f_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DhruvaCommand%3C%2Fa%3E%20forge%20thunderstorms%20by%20honing%20skills%20beyond%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FZojilla%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Zojilla%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pass%20to%20refine%20professional%20skills%20and%20enhance%20operational%20readiness.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9D%91%AC%F0%9D%92%97%F0%9D%92%86%F0%9D%92%93%F0%9D%92%9A%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeOhau4aa9X%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FeOhau4aa9X%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NORTHERN%20COMMAND%20-%20INDIAN%20ARMY%20(%40NorthernComd_IA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNorthernComd_IA%2Fstatus%2F1728991921354441043%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20loaded%20shells%20in%20the%20artillery%20guns%20and%20after%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20a%20deafening%20sound%20echoed%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20field%20guns%20%26quot%3Bforged%20thunderstorms%20amidst%20frozen%20whispers%20of%20high%20altitudes%26quot%3B.%20The%20exercise%20was%20conducted%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20a%20Brigadier-rank%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20drill%20was%20conducted%20post%20dusk%20and%20the%20dark%20sky%20lit%20up%20with%20ammunition%20pounding%20on%20the%20crest%20of%20rocky%20mountains%20near%20the%20pass.%20The%20pass%20is%20strategically%20important%20since%20it%20lies%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LOC)%20and%20is%20the%20lifeline%20which%20connects%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EZojila's%20Tryst%20With%20Battles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%201947-48%20India-Pakistan%20war%2C%20the%20pass%20fell%20to%20the%20Pakistani%20raiders%20and%20was%20vital%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20Leh%20and%20had%20to%20be%20captured%20before%20the%20winter.%20The%20army%20launched%20Operation%20Bison%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20Zojila%20Pass.%20Stuart%20Mk-V%20light%20tanks%20from%20the%207%20Cavalry%20were%20dismantled%20and%20then%20transported%20from%20Srinagar%20to%20Baltal%20and%20were%20reassembled%20for%20deployment.%20Mule%20tracks%20were%20improved%20from%20Baltal%20to%20Zojila.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20tanks%20were%20operated%20at%20such%20height%20and%20the%20Army's%20armour%20and%20infantry%20troops%20successfully%20captured%20Zojila%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%201999%20Kargil%20conflict%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army's%20access%20to%20the%20Zojila%20pass%20was%20threatened%20by%20Pakistan%20after%20it%20took%20control%20of%20several%20posts%20overlooking%20the%20Srinagar-Leh%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Artillery%20regiment%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20turning%20the%20tide%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20Kargil%20and%20the%20newly%20acquired%20Bofors%20gun%20provided%20vital%20support%20to%20the%20infantry.%20The%20'Batalik%20Bombers'%20were%20deployed%20during%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701075180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F26l0u834_army-artilley-_625x300_27_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-armys-artillery-guns-forge-thunderstorms-near-zojila-pass-4609672%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Army%20%26quot%3Bforged%20thunderstorms%26quot%3B%20at%2011%2C500%20feet%20near%20the%20Zojila%20Pass%20to%20stay%20battle-ready%20as%20the%20harsh%20winter%20set%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-armys-artillery-guns-forge-thunderstorms-near-zojila-pass-4609672%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-armys-artillery-guns-forge-thunderstorms-near-zojila-pass-4609672%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F