the%20Mizoram%20Kohhran%20Hruaitute%20Committee%20(MKHC)%2C%20a%20conglomerate%20of%2015%20major%20churches%20of%20the%20state%2C%20urged%20all%20churches%20this%20past%20Saturday%20(November%2025)%20to%20organise%20prayers%20during%20the%20Sunday%20church%20service%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20from%20God%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20counting%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20Presbyterian%20Church%2C%20the%20largest%20denomination%20in%20the%20state%2C%20also%20separately%20urged%20its%20members%20to%20hold%20prayers%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20date%20of%20counting%20is%20changed%2C%20said%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.themizorampost.net%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20five-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20NGO%20Coordination%20Committee%20(NGOCC)%2C%20an%20Aizawl-based%20umbrella%20body%20of%20NGOs%20and%20student%20organisations%2C%20has%20been%20staying%20put%20in%20New%20Delhi%20since%20the%20past%20week%20to%20seek%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20(CEC)%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20delegation%20has%20come%20to%20the%20national%20Capital%20after%20pleas%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%20went%20unheard.%20Those%20pleas%20were%20made%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20CEC%20in%20New%20Delhi%20had%20announced%20the%20election%20schedule%20in%20the%20state%20along%20with%20December%203%20as%20the%20common%20date%20for%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20all%20the%20five%20poll-bound%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENews%20reports%20said%20the%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20office%20has%20given%20time%20to%20the%20delegation%20on%20November%2028.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20SEC%20has%20made%20all%20arrangements%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20counting%20on%20December%203%20as%20scheduled.%20A%20%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20quoting%20additional%20chief%20election%20officer%20H.%20Lianzela%20said%20more%20than%204%2C000%20counting%20personnel%20would%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20counting%20exercise%20which%20was%20to%20begin%20at%208%20am.%20In%20all%2C%2013%20counting%20centres%20would%20be%20set%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20November%2029%2C%20a%20full%20dress%20rehearsal%20of%20the%20counting%20exercise%20would%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20SEC%20for%20smooth%20conduct%20on%20the%20designated%20day%2C%20state%20chief%20election%20officer%20Madhup%20Vyas%20told%20reporters%20in%20Aizwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701073505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14184445%2Fpexels-m-15226359.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmizoram-churches-pray-change-counting-date-assembly-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20counting%20is%20scheduled%20on%20December%203%2C%20a%20Sunday%20and%20the%20day%20of%20worship%20for%20Christians.%20Several%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20Church%20have%20asked%20the%20ECI%20to%20postpone%20the%20counting%20day%20for%20Mizoram%20by%20a%20day%20or%20two.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmizoram-churches-pray-change-counting-date-assembly-polls%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Audi%2C%20Maruti%20Suzuki%20to%20hike%20prices%20of%20its%20cars%20from%20January%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701073262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F08%2Ffull%2F1696788646-0695.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fafter-audi-maruti-suzuki-to-hike-prices-of-its-car