ambie%20heroes%20ingredients%20grown%20in%20Meghalaya%20%E2%80%94%20like%20fiddlehead%20ferns%2C%20elephant%20apple%2C%20elephant%20foot%20yams%2C%20purple%20yams%2C%20Indian%20sorrel%2C%20fish%20mint%20leaves%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohiong%3C%2Fem%3E%20(blackberry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohplhang%20(%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20root%20vegetable)%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20makes%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E%20using%20ingredients%20like%20brinjal%20and%20dry%20fish%2C%20fermented%20fish%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20dried%20roselle%20with%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Epura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(rice%20flour)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejadoh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20%3Cem%3EKhasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20rice%20recipe)%2C%20beef%20trotter%20soup%2C%20muskmelon%20and%20pork%20gravy%20dish%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20appreciated%20by%20many%2C%20she%20also%20faced%20vicious%20trolling%20and%20hate.%20Trolls%20ridiculed%20her%20for%20cooking%20outdoors%2C%20the%20food%20she%20cooked%2C%20and%20even%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20wore%20slippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20really%20harsh%20comments.%20People%20said%20things%20like%20%E2%80%9CYour%20food%20looks%20like%20dog%20food%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20you%20wearing%20those%20slippers%3F%E2%80%9D.%20I%20cook%20outside%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20electricity%20most%20of%20the%20time%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20our%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trolling%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20she%20considered%20quitting%20social%20media%20due%20to%20the%20excessive%20negativity.%20All%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20do%20was%20showcase%20her%20home%2C%20surroundings%20and%20food.%20Realising%20that%20she%20would%20let%20the%20naysayers%20win%20if%20she%20gave%20up%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20overcome%20the%20hate%20by%20growing%20a%20thick%20skin.%20She%20focused%20on%20the%20positive%20comments%2C%20which%20were%20also%20many%20in%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20accept%20that%20there%20will%20be%20negativity%20and%20people%20trying%20to%20pull%20you%20down.%20What%20matters%20is%20that%20you%20should%20believe%20in%20what%20you%20do.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20let%20the%20haters%20win.%20What%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20is%20trying%20to%20showcase%20my%20cuisine%20and%20break%20the%20stereotypes%20associated%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20overcame%20the%20xenophobia%20and%20became%20a%20harbinger%20for%20many%20more%20YouTubers%20from%20the%20Northeast%2C%20which%20led%20to%20her%20cementing%20a%20position%20in%20MasterChef%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life%20to%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCgJotPrDIeJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCgJotPrDIeJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCgJotPrDIeJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Nambie%20Jessica%20Marak%20(%40eatyourkappa)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20YouTube%20channel%20was%20flourishing%2C%20she%20had%20to%20move%20back%20home%20as%20her%20mother%20was%20ill.%20In%202019%2C%20she%20packed%20her%20bags%20and%20moved%20to%20Upper%20Rangsa%20with%20her%20infant%20daughter.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20also%20a%20teacher%2C%20packed%20his%20bags%2C%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20two%20most%20educated%20people%20in%20the%20entire%20village%20of%20150%20people%2C%20they%20were%20soon%20presented%20with%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20change%2C%20when%20a%20private%20school%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20village%20was%20about%20to%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20the%20person%20running%20the%20school%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20manage%20the%20school.%20He%20abandoned%20the%20school%20and%20the%20children%20and%20left.%20The%20village%20head%20came%20to%20us%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20help%20as%20it%20is%20the%20only%20school%20for%20the%20children%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffered%20a%20school%20on%20a%20plate%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20help%20villagers%2C%20the%20couple%20took%20up%20the%20challenge.%20They%20adopted%20the%20school%20and%20the%2019%20students%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20village%20sits%20near%20the%20border%2C%20and%20with%20poor%20roads%2C%20commuting%20to%20schools%20outside%20daily%20isn%E2%80%99t%20feasible.%20If%20this%20school%20closes%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20disrupt%20many%20farmers%E2%80%99%20lives.%20They%20might%20need%20to%20move%20to%20Assam%2C%20straining%20resources%20and%20losing%20their%20income.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20to%20worry%20about%20where%20their%20kids%20go%20to%20school.%20We%20only%20want%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20farms%2C%E2%80%